---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ScopingForm from "../components/ScopingForm";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Get Started | Free Website Quote | doticrosst"
  description="Answer a few quick questions about your business and get a clear website quote within one working day. No obligation, no jargon."
>
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-light">Get Started</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl">Get started with a free website quote</h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
          Answer a few quick questions and we'll come back with a clear scope and quote. Takes about 2 minutes. No obligation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">How the scoping form works</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Getting started with doticrosst takes about two minutes. The form below asks a few
          straightforward questions about your business, what you need from a website, and
          your timeline. There is no jargon and no trick questions. Once you submit, we review
          your answers and come back with a clear, fixed-price quote within one working day.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          This free website quote covers everything -- design, build, local SEO setup, and
          hosting. If you want ongoing support after launch, we will include pricing for that
          too. There is zero obligation to proceed. We send you the quote, you think about it,
          and you decide. No follow-up calls unless you want them.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">What happens after you get started</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          After you submit the form, we will email you with our initial thoughts, a clear
          scope of work, and a fixed price. If anything needs clarifying, we will arrange a
          short call -- typically 15 to 20 minutes. Once you give the green light, your
          website build starts immediately and is usually live within two to three weeks.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Throughout the build, you will see progress and have the chance to give feedback
          before anything goes live. We do not disappear into a black box for three weeks
          and then reveal something you did not ask for. Every project is collaborative,
          transparent, and built to your requirements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ScopingForm client:load />

      <form name="website-scoping" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" hidden>
        <input name="business_name" /><input name="industry" /><input name="locations" />
        <input name="years_in_business" /><input name="has_website" /><input name="website_url" />
        <input name="website_platform" /><input name="has_google_business" /><input name="google_maps_url" />
        <input name="instagram" /><input name="facebook" /><input name="project_type" />
        <input name="pages_needed" /><input name="needs_booking" /><input name="needs_gallery" />
        <input name="needs_blog" /><input name="needs_seo" /><input name="budget_range" />
        <input name="timeline" /><input name="anything_else" /><input name="name" />
        <input name="email" /><input name="phone" />
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
